1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Lactate isn’t just waste; it’s a key player in our bodies.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,400
For years, scientists viewed lactate as a byproduct of exercise.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:11,200
But new research is challenging that idea.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:16,000
Lactate actually fuels our muscles and brain, helping us adapt and recover.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,800
Studies show that lactate can improve endurance and even enhance cognitive function.

6
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,200
It’s not just a waste product!

7
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:29,600
So next time you hear ‘lactic acid’, remember it’s more of a fuel than a waste.

8
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,600
Curious about more science myths?

9
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:33,200
Follow for more insights!
